# 💰 Smart Finance Tracker

A full-stack **MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js)** web application that helps users efficiently manage their personal finances by tracking income, expenses, budgets, and financial activities through an intuitive dashboard.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

Smart Finance Tracker is designed to simplify personal finance management by allowing users to securely record their income and expenses, monitor their financial balance, and analyze spending patterns. The application provides a responsive interface, secure authentication, and real-time updates to help users make better financial decisions.

---

## ✨ Features

* 🔐 Secure User Authentication (JWT)
* 👤 User Registration and Login
* 💰 Add, Edit, and Delete Income
* 💸 Add, Edit, and Delete Expenses
* 📊 Interactive Financial Dashboard
* 📈 Income & Expense Analytics
* 📂 Category-wise Expense Management
* 📝 Transaction History
* 🔍 Search and Filter Transactions
* 📱 Responsive User Interface
* ⚡ Real-Time Data Updates
* 🗄️ Secure MongoDB Database Integration

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend

* React.js
* JavaScript (ES6+)
* HTML5
* CSS3
* Bootstrap / Tailwind CSS (based on project setup)
* Axios

### Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js
* JWT Authentication
* bcrypt.js
* Mongoose

### Database

* MongoDB

